WEBVTT

00:08:28.196 --> 00:08:33.323
This is inexplicable without the presence
of intelligent beings.

00:08:33.347 --> 00:08:35.244
And if they then asked themselves,

00:08:35.268 --> 00:08:40.720
"Well, this influence, the influence that
affected the atmosphere of that planet,

00:08:40.744 --> 00:08:42.799
could it possibly affect us?"

00:08:42.823 --> 00:08:45.371
And the answer is yes,

00:08:45.395 --> 00:08:51.760
because the issue of whether
a spaceship can get there

00:08:51.784 --> 00:08:54.014
is a matter of what we decide to do.

00:08:54.038 --> 00:08:56.593
And it's also a matter
of the laws of physics.

00:08:57.315 --> 00:09:01.053
CA: So, David, I think it's important,
almost, to having this conversation